        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The `aprovar_rejeitar_pecas_admin` function has been defined. Now, I need to demonstrate its usage by first registering an administrator and then calling the function to either approve or reject parts for an existing service. This involves inserting an admin into the database, calling the `aprovar_rejeitar_pecas_admin` function, and finally verifying the database state.\n",
