        "id": "cb60e59d"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "I need to implement the `get_servicos_mecanico` function as per the instructions. This function will query the `servicos` table using the provided `id_mecanico` to retrieve all service details, including `pecas_sugeridas_mecanico`, `pecas_aprovadas_admin`, `status_solicitacao_pecas`, and `comissao_mecanico_porcentagem`.\n",
