        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The next step is to implement the `verificar_comissao_mecanico` function. To make the function more robust and aligned with the instruction's mention of `permissoes_json` for a global commission, I will first update João Silva's permissions in the database to include a `comissao_percentual` field. This requires a small helper function to update the `permissoes_json` for an existing user. Then, I will create the `verificar_comissao_mecanico` function which will first check `permissoes_json` for this global percentage, and if not present, it will check `servicos` table.\n",
        "\n"
