        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "To demonstrate that a mechanic can adjust piece suggestions while the status is 'Pendente', I need to create a new service, have the mechanic make an initial suggestion, and then make a second, different suggestion for the same new service. After that, I will verify the service to show the updated suggestions, thus addressing instructions 5 and 6.\n",
