      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "59757876"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "I need to modify the `aprovar_rejeitar_pecas_admin` function to handle the new 'marca_aprovada' field. This involves updating the function's logic to retrieve and display suggested parts, validate the presence of 'marca_aprovada' during approval, and serialize the approved parts with the brand information into the `pecas_aprovadas_admin` column.\n",
