        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Now that the administrator has viewed the pending requests, the next step is to approve the parts for the service, selecting a specific brand for each item, as per instruction 6. I will use the `aprovar_rejeitar_pecas_admin` function and then `verificar_servico` to confirm the update as per instruction 7.\n",
