        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Now that the database schema has been updated with the 'ordens_servico' table, I need to update the `registar_colaborador` function to reflect this change. Although `registar_colaborador` doesn't directly interact with `servicos`, I will include it and ensure all subsequent functions use the new table name, starting with `registar_servico`.\n",
