      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "21ded4b3"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The subtask requires updating the `registar_servico` function to use the new `ordens_servico` table, initialize the `valor_comissao_mecanico` column, and update print messages. I will provide the complete updated function.\n",
