      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5fadad7a"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The previous steps successfully registered a mechanic and administrator, created a service, handled part suggestions from the mechanic, and approved them by the administrator, setting service value and commission. Now, I need to execute instruction 8 to verify the updated service details, specifically confirming the 'pecas_aprovadas_admin', 'valor_total', 'comissao_mecanico_porcentagem', and 'valor_comissao_mecanico' columns are correctly updated in the database.\n",
