        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The `ValueError` occurred because `servico_verificado[13]`, which holds the string value for `status_solicitacao_pecas`, was being formatted as a float. The `valor_comissao_mecanico` is actually at index 14 of the `servico_verificado` tuple. Additionally, the parsing of `pecas_aprovadas_admin_parsed` was incorrectly using index 11 (pecas_sugeridas_mecanico) instead of index 12 (pecas_aprovadas_admin). I will correct these index references in the print statements and the JSON parsing.\n",
